WARN 4: Public Bucket Allows Listing
  Level: WARN
  Description: Detects public storage buckets with a broad SELECT policy on `storage.objects`, which allows clients to list all files in the bucket.
  Categories: SECURITY
  How to fix (visit the link to see what to do!): https://supabase.com/docs/guides/database/database-linter?lint=0025_public_bucket_allows_listing

